{"word":"ὑψόω","slug":"ὑψόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑψόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὕψος\">ὕψος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘cause to move from a position to one that is higher’, <b>lift upward <a href='B:500 3:14'>J 3:14</a>; <a href='B:500 8:28'>8:28</a>; <a href='B:500 12:32'>12:32</a>, <a href='B:500 12:34'>34</a>; <a href='B:510 2:33'>Ac 2:33</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to be higher in status’, <b>elevate, exalt <a href='B:470 11:23'>Mt 11:23</a>; <a href='B:470 23:12'>23:12</a>; <a href='B:490 1:52'>Lk 1:52</a>; <a href='B:490 14:11'>14:11</a>; <a href='B:510 5:31'>Ac 5:31</a>; <a href='B:510 13:17'>13:17</a>; <a href='B:540 11:7'>2 Cor 11:7</a>; <a href='B:660 4:10'>Js 4:10</a>; <a href='B:670 5:6'>1 Pt 5:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὕψος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὕψωμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}